 & = & \frac{p_{0}}{4\pi\epsilon_{0}}\left[2\cos\theta\hat{\mathbf{r}}+\sin\theta\hat{\boldsymbol{\theta}}\right]\frac{1}{r^{3}}\cos\omega_{0}\left(t-\frac{r}{c}\right)
